{"tid":1504692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想見到手足ge麻煩入黎睇下 可唔可以唔好重覆同樣既錯誤","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:43:31.000Z","uid":196536,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a69628e2bab3fae8b238481b078dc3c07f17843f","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇直播又見到堆手足比人拉 我諗好多人都慶過火屎<br />\n慶既原因唔只係因為班黑警<br />\n更加係因為其實好多都可以避免<br />\n頭先係荃灣, D示威者係咁企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHEDbND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHEDbND.png&h=b3df82c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n群體人數越大 要移動就越難 班狗越逼近 示威者就越危險<br />\n當速龍衝埋黎 我敢講有90%既示威者都唔能夠全速跑走<br />\n其他巴打講左幾十次 我唔爭在講多次<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該留番D位比前線同其他手足走好唔好呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zdVyK8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzdVyK8v.png&h=1194f0c0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong>最後排要清楚見到前排發生咩事</strong><br />\n如果你發覺你個位唔係好睇到前面有冇狗衝緊埋黎<br />\n唔該搵過第二個位<br />\n或者走<br />\n以後係前線 見到D人開始企埋一舊<br />\n<strong>大家幫下手唔好怕醜 叫大家企番個方陣 解釋下個原因</strong><br />\n一個都不能少呢個唔係口號 真係要做<br />\n最後我屌晒D花生友老母 我地幾百個手足被捕都係你累番黎!!<br />\n<br />\n抗爭已經兩個幾月 要進化 唔好再比班狗放題啦<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人加油, 光復香港, 時代革命</div>"},{"pid":"5783ab84392a1d8e23e22e789657a9edec6ed8c1","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"好累啦真係<br />\n有一半人都可以唔使坐臭格架"},{"pid":"47d27a9a0a64701984d00cce68901ab7ff5b8a10","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"求下大家幫手推下<br />\n勇武已經所剩無幾"},{"pid":"5e088a2862b7f64bd206bc27793923415851d8dd","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c586f15f3b94cf6295fad39d5078ceb1df35bfe8","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"我自推一百次<br />\n1"},{"pid":"e1482d9ad09203ff53e92d48f2fe7d09db0def18","tid":1504692,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7722a01254154213196afb6fe0e0d9478bed2016","tid":1504692,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e2068c8bfac2490941a5b448cba32f14c40dc968","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n<br />\n生性啊手足"},{"pid":"26b186f92c0bcab54ad45dabea4871451f70cd85","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"44e07f5c50baa26c8efd5ae649ee23f73bef8a44","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9bf6bf93496b767b343d04b644df981b77dc6d54","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"ab8cdc0769cb689a15161c51b56de93cf3fce554","tid":1504692,"uid":217306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46dcee0a62d3a4682b03b5a3305dc9e74609c3c9","tid":1504692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507550c6c91aeb899b8263ed7b8a5ef9b49f9523","tid":1504692,"uid":19653